  "notes": [
    "All 27 POIs come from the JSONP API endpoint newapi?graveyard=18",
    "Marker icons are numbered maker_1.png through maker_50.png (typo 'maker' in original)",
    "Markers are created in a loop: grave index d -> marker(d+1) icon assignment",
    "Map requires cookie consent (mapSettings=mapOn) before rendering",
    "graveGroups array referenced in JS for carousel display grouping (by berufkat category), but all graves appear in the flat graves array for map markers",
    "Coordinates for ID 397 (Hanussen) showed minor variation between graveyard API and individual grave API; individual grave API values used (52.39061, 13.18382)",
    "The 'ehrengrab' field is explicitly present in the API (0 or 1)",
    "No GeoJSON endpoint found - all data served as JSONP objects",
    "No additional external JS files detected - all logic is inline"
  ]
